00:23:16.720 --> 00:23:19.120
N-Ne oldu, Rio Efendi?

00:23:23.090 --> 00:23:24.530
Ne oluyor?

00:23:24.530 --> 00:23:25.660
Bu da ne?

00:23:25.660 --> 00:23:27.130
